WEBVTT

00:00.343 --> 00:01.859
Previously on "Heartland"...

00:01.912 --> 00:04.380
Let's do it.
Let's move in together.

00:04.415 --> 00:06.349
I don't think you understand
what I'm trying to say.

00:06.383 --> 00:08.485
I wanna buy this place
on my own.

00:09.499 --> 00:11.254
- Yes!
- You got us out!

00:11.288 --> 00:13.423
We did it! We did it!
We got out!

00:13.457 --> 00:15.692
Oh my gosh! Oh my gosh... Um...

00:17.661 --> 00:19.262
- Ah! There's my dad. Let's go.
- Yeah.

00:19.296 --> 00:21.931
- I'm giving you the horse.
- You know it's not that easy.

00:21.966 --> 00:25.401
I screwed everything up.
I know that.

00:25.436 --> 00:26.870
I loved you, I really did.

00:26.904 --> 00:29.606
Yeah. I guess that's
what makes this so difficult.

